     C*                    MOVE *BLANK    @TSYO
     C*                    Z-ADD0         @TBAN
     C*                    MOVE *BLANK    @SYUK
     C*                    MOVE *BLANK    @KAKO
     C*                    MOVE *BLANK    @SYOT
     C                     Z-ADD0         CNT
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    MSG
     C                     ENDSR
**  CMT
